oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Crescent Drive-In Schedule
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Drive-in theaters; Theaters;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Two color window card (blue on orange) announcing Crescent Drive In Theatre's showing of the Sins of Rachel Cade on May 14, 15, and 16; The Sundowners on May 17, 18, and 19; and Battle Cry with Five Branded Women on May 20.
